title: #92Noon! Lavelle Neal/Ben Leber/Korzo
description: PA opens the show with some live sounds and commentary from the NYFC vs Philadelphia MLS game.  Lavelle Neal calls in to talk the Twins intra-team games that took place at training. Ben Leber joins PA in studio for an hours worth of NFL conversation.  Plus, fill-in producer & afro extraordinaire Maxx Fuller gives his top 5 heavyweight fights of all time!
